Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about text translation and language processing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper focuses on extracting visual features from videos to aid in translation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses a state-of-the-art transformer-based approach. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the use of visual information to improve translation quality. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with a multimodal approach to translation using both text and visual features.
